rie von Niklas Luhmann orientiert.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 4aArbeit. 4aBildwissenschaft. 4aFamiliensoziologie. 4aGender Studies. 4aGender. 4aGeschlecht. 4aImage. 4aMedien. 4aMediensoziologie. 4aSoziologie. 4aSoziologische Theorie. 4aVereinbarkeitsdiskurs. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Gender Studies.2bisacsh  aGender Studies.  aGender.  aSociological Theory.  aSociology of Family.  aSociology of Media.  aSociology.  aVisual Studies.  aWork.1 aAlbrecht, Maren.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Highlight Collection Complete Package 2010-2013z9783110352856oZDB-23-TSO08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Highlight Collection Sozialw. 2010-2013z9783110370713oZDB-23-TSW08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript: Complete eBook-Package 2013z9783110401219oZDB-23-TGP40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839424711423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839424711/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-TGPb2013  aZDB-23-TSOc2010d2013  aZDB-23-TSWc2010d2013